Annual contribution levels are noted in the donor lists. These levels are designated by the accompanying key:

ILLINOIS COLLEGE SOCIETY

Beecher Club :: $10,000 and above

The Yale Band Club :: $5,000 to $9,999

Ellis Club :: $2,500 to $4,999

Lippincott Club :: $1,000 to $2,499

BLUE & WHITE CIRCLE

President’s Club :: $500 to $999

College Club :: $250 to $499

Century Club :: $100 to $249

Patrons Club :: $99 and under

* Deceased with a funded memorial membership // • Donor who has funded memorial membership // Number following name indicates the total number of years of giving since 1957
